## 1. PROJECT OVERVIEW

**Project Name:** Aesthetic Tech Store
**Type:** Full-Stack E-Commerce Web Application
**Domain:** Technology & Electronics Retail
**Target Market:** Bangladesh (with scalability for international expansion)
**Architecture:** Multi-role, dual-dashboard system with three distinct user roles

**Core Value Proposition:**
A smart, aesthetically pleasing e-commerce platform specializing in electronics, PC components, networking gear, and tech accessories. The platform differentiates through a seamless PC Builder tool, MegaCoin loyalty rewards, comprehensive coupon system, and a professional delivery management pipeline.

