## 2. USER ROLES & AUTHENTICATION SYSTEM

### 2.1 Three-Role Architecture

| Role | Purpose | Access Level |
|------|---------|-------------|
| **Admin** | Store management, inventory, orders, analytics | Full system access |
| **Buyer (User)** | Browse, purchase, track orders, loyalty rewards | Customer-facing features |
| **Delivery Man** | Pickup, deliver, update delivery status | Delivery pipeline only |

### 2.2 Authentication & Authorization
- Email/password registration and login for all roles
- Social login (Google, Facebook) for Buyers
- Role-based access control (RBAC) with JWT tokens
- Password reset via email OTP
- Account verification via email/SMS OTP
- Separate login portals for each role with role detection
- Session management with automatic timeout
- Profile management (avatar, contact info, address book)

### 2.3 Registration Flows
- **Buyer Registration:** Name, Email, Phone, Password, Address (Division, District, Thana)
- **Delivery Man Registration:** Name, Email, Phone, NID, Driving License, Vehicle Info, Photo, Emergency Contact
- **Admin Registration:** Invitation-only by super-admin

